{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"tool_JxX2ix7JJfGLEPSN036Vnl1Q","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"Dinoki AI companion pixel pet pricing Pro features\"\n\nSearch results for query: Dinoki AI companion pixel pet pricing Dinoki AI companion Pro features Dinoki AI companion pixel pet pricing Pro\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"Dinoki - Privacy-First AI Assistant for Desktop\",\"url\":\"https://dinoki.ai/\"},{\"title\":\"Getting Started | Dinoki Documentation\",\"url\":\"https://docs.dinoki.ai/getting-started\"},{\"title\":\"Building Dinoki: Native AI companion for Mac/Windows\",\"url\":\"https://www.indiehackers.com/post/building-dinoki-native-ai-companion-for-mac-windows-4228efd94a\"},{\"title\":\"Features | Dinoki Documentation\",\"url\":\"https://docs.dinoki.ai/features\"},{\"title\":\"Dinoki Documentation\",\"url\":\"https://docs.dinoki.ai/\"},{\"title\":\"Dinoki: A 5MB AI Companion That Lives on Your Mac Desktop — No Servers, No Tracking\",\"url\":\"https://alternativeto.net/software/dinoki/about/\"},{\"title\":\"Features, Age Range, Battery Life, and Price Compared\",\"url\":\"https://keyirobot.com/blogs/buying-guide/electronic-pet-buying-guide-features-age-range-battery-life-and-price-compared?srsltid=AfmBOoo40DDnYAqNqO8R34U_0yfCXlGzVNG7byxFtCBjYaWHbkfeuPTX\"},{\"title\":\"AI Companion Pricing Guide 2026: Every Platform Compared\",\"url\":\"https://aicompanionguides.com/blog/ai-companion-pricing-guide-2026/\"},{\"title\":\"Configuration | Dinoki Documentation\",\"url\":\"https://docs.dinoki.ai/configuration\"},{\"title\":\"Dinoki Labs\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/dinoki-ai\"},{\"title\":\"Using Dinoki | Dinoki Documentation\",\"url\":\"https://docs.dinoki.ai/using-dinoki\"}]\n\nHere are the search results for **Dinoki AI companion pixel pet pricing and Pro features**:\n\n## Pricing\n\n| Plan | Price | Details |\n|------|-------|---------|\n| **Free** | $0 | Full chat mode, offline AI, persistent memory |\n| **Pro** | **$25.00 one-time purchase** | Lifetime unlock—**not a subscription** |\n| **Trial** | 7 days | Free Pro trial included with download |\n\n## Pro Features\n\n**Desktop Characters (Pixel Pets)**\n- **4 animated companions**: Dinoki 🦕 (free), TomatoBoy 🍅, PigPig 🐷, and Fuegato 🐱\n- Characters walk, jump, dance, show emotions, and interact with speech bubbles on your desktop\n- **Multiple instances**: Run several characters simultaneously\n- Custom personalities and activity levels (low/medium/high)\n- Adjustable sizes and screen positions\n\n**Agent Mode**\n- Autonomous background task execution\n- \"Set it and forget it\" automation\n- Persistent goals with progress updates\n- Smart tool selection\n\n**Premium Tools**\n- **Web & Research**: Smart search, web browsing, deep research\n- **Productivity**: File saving, reminders, screenshots\n- **Communication**: Slack integration, Gmail management, auto-replies\n- **Market Data**: Weather, stock prices, crypto tracking\n\n**Advanced Capabilities**\n- MCP (Model Context Protocol) integration for connecting with other AIs and tools\n- Tool permissions per instance\n- Priority support\n\n## Key Differentiators\n\n- **Truly native app**: 6MB on macOS (SwiftUI), 69MB on Windows (WPF)—no Electron bloat\n- **Privacy-first**: No backend, no tracking, runs fully offline with local models (Ollama/Osaurus)\n- **Retro pixel-art aesthetic**: Described as \"Tamagotchi vibes + GPT smarts\"\n- **One-time payment**: No monthly subscription required for Pro\n\nYou can download it at [dinoki.ai](https://dinoki.ai) and documentation is available at [docs.dinoki.ai](https://docs.dinoki.ai).\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"86674783-7214-4236-b263-658ed93960b9","uuid":"c53dedce-c4d8-4633-a1c7-608d8ebc08a0","timestamp":"2026-05-20T09:34:43.719Z","tool_use_result":{"query":"Dinoki AI companion pixel pet pricing Pro f