noki 🦕 (free), TomatoBoy 🍅, PigPig 🐷, and Fuegato 🐱\n- Characters walk, jump, dance, show emotions, and interact with speech bubbles on your desktop\n- **Multiple instances**: Run several characters simultaneously\n- Custom personalities and activity levels (low/medium/high)\n- Adjustable sizes and screen positions\n\n**Agent Mode**\n- Autonomous background task execution\n- \"Set it and forget it\" automation\n- Persistent goals with progress updates\n- Smart tool selection\n\n**Premium Tools**\n- **Web & Research**: Smart search, web browsing, deep research\n- **Productivity**: File saving, reminders, screenshots\n- **Communication**: Slack integration, Gmail management, auto-replies\n- **Market Data**: Weather, stock prices, crypto tracking\n\n**Advanced Capabilities**\n- MCP (Model Context Protocol) integration for connecting with other AIs and tools\n- Tool permissions per instance\n- Priority support\n\n## Key Differentiators\n\n- **Truly native app**: 6MB on macOS (SwiftUI), 69MB on Windows (WPF)—no Electron bloat\n- **Privacy-first**: No backend, no tracking, runs fully offline with local models (Ollama/Osaurus)\n- **Retro pixel-art aesthetic**: Described as \"Tamagotchi vibes + GPT smarts\"\n- **One-time payment**: No monthly subscription required for Pro\n\nYou can download it at [dinoki.ai](https://dinoki.ai) and documentation is available at [docs.dinoki.ai](https://docs.dinoki.ai)."],"durationSeconds":45.39406816700002,"searchCount":1}}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"tool_DbcoWHeFFn05JfpVUI3eBPPS","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"Dinoki AI download macOS Windows GitHub releases\"\n\nSearch results for query: Dinoki AI macOS download Dinoki AI Windows release Dinoki AI GitHub releases\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"Osaurus | MCP Servers\",\"url\":\"https://lobehub.com/de/mcp/osaurus-ai-osaurus\"},{\"title\":\"Dinoki Labs\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/dinoki-ai\"},{\"title\":\"Trendshift - Ask AI\",\"url\":\"https://trendshift.io/admin/repository/ask-ai/15476\"},{\"title\":\"SkillsLLM - AI Skills Marketplace\",\"url\":\"https://skillsllm.com/skill/osaurus\"},{\"title\":\"Mac App 'osaurus' v0.6.9 Download\",\"url\":\"https://macupdater.net/app_updates/appinfo/com.dinoki.osaurus/index.html\"},{\"title\":\"dinoki-ai/osaurus\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/dinoki-ai/osaurus\"},{\"title\":\"Dinoki Documentation\",\"url\":\"https://docs.dinoki.ai/\"},{\"title\":\"Getting Started | Dinoki Documentation\",\"url\":\"https://docs.dinoki.ai/getting-started\"},{\"title\":\"GitHub - dinoki-ai/tweaks: AI-powered text enhancement for macOS\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/dinoki-ai/tweaks\"},{\"title\":\"Support | Dinoki Documentation\",\"url\":\"https://docs.dinoki.ai/support\"},{\"title\":\"Features | Dinoki Documentation\",\"url\":\"https://docs.dinoki.ai/features\"},{\"title\":\"Osaurus挑战Ollama？Mac本地大模型新王者登场\",\"url\":\"https://www.xugj520.cn/archives/osaurus-mac-llm.html\"},{\"title\":\"Osaurus vs Ollama: The Ultimate Apple Silicon LLM Server Showdown\",\"url\":\"https://www.xugj520.cn/en/archives/osaurus-vs-ollama-showdown.html\"},{\"title\":\"GitHub - dinoki-ai/osaurus-macos-use\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/dinoki-ai/osaurus-macos-use\"}]\n\nBased on my search, here's what I found for **Dinoki AI** downloads across macOS, Windows, and GitHub releases:\n\n---\n\n## 🖥️ Dinoki Desktop App (The AI Companion)\n\n**Dinoki** is the main desktop pixel AI companion app. It supports **both macOS and Windows**.\n\n### Downloads\n\n| Platform | Download | Size |\n|----------|----------|------|\n| **macOS (Apple Silicon)** | [Download DMG](https://docs.dinoki.ai/) | ~6 MB |\n| **macOS (Intel)** | [Download DMG](https://docs.dinoki.ai/) | ~6 MB |\n| **Windows** | Download MSIX Installer | ~69 MB |\n| **Windows (Portable)** | Download ZIP | ~69 MB |\n\n**Official download page:** [docs.dinoki.ai](https://docs.dinoki.ai/) or [dinoki.ai](https://dinoki.ai)\n\n---\n\n## 🦕 Osaurus (Local AI Runtime)\n\n**Osaurus** is the local LLM server that powers offline AI in Dinoki. **Note: This is macOS-only (Apple Silicon)**.\n\n### Installation Options\n\n**Homebrew (Recommended):**\n```bash\nbrew install --cask osaurus\n```\n\n**GitHub Releases DMG:**\n- Download `Osaurus.dmg` from the releases page\n- Drag to Applications folder\n- Requires macOS 15.5+ and Apple Silicon (M1/M2/M3)\n\n### GitHub Repository (Moved!)\n⚠️ **Important:** The Osaurus repository has moved:\n- **Old:** `github.com/dinoki-ai/osaurus` (archived)\n- **New:** [`github.com/osaurus-ai/osaurus`](https://github.com/osaurus-ai/osaurus) ← Active development & releases live here\n\n---\n\n## 🐙 GitHub Repositories (Dinoki Labs)\n\n| Repo | Description | Platform |\n|------|-------------|----------|\n| [`dinoki-ai`](https://github.com/dinoki-ai) | Main organization page | — |\n| [`osaurus-ai/osaurus`](https://github.com/osaurus-ai/osaurus) | AI edge runtime / local LLM server | macOS (Apple Silicon) |\n| [`dinoki-ai/tweaks`](https://github.com/dinoki-ai/tweaks) | AI-powered text enhancement for macOS | macOS |\n| [`dinoki-ai/osaurus-macos-use`](https://github.com/dinoki-ai/osaurus-macos-use) | macOS UI automation plugin for Osaurus | macOS |\n\n---\n\n## ⚡ Quick Setup Summary\n\n1. **For macOS users:** Download Dinoki (6MB DMG) + install Osaurus for local AI (`brew install --cask osaurus`)\n2. **For Windows users:** Download the MSIX installer (69MB) or Portable ZIP\n3. **For local/离线 AI:** Osaurus is required but is **macOS Apple Silicon only**. Windows users can use cloud providers (OpenAI, OpenRouter, etc.)\n\n---\n\n**Note:** Windows users looking for the Dinoki app should check the documentation site directly, as the search results indicate a separate Windows repository exists but point to [docs.dinoki.ai](https://docs.dinoki.ai/) as the primary download hub.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"86674783-7214-4236-b263-658ed93960b9","uuid":"3ff5907d-b213-4772-b1cf-4ac2695b3c3a","timestamp":"2026-05-20T09:34:50.116Z","tool_use_result":{"query":"Dinoki AI download macOS Windows GitHub releases","results":["Search results for query: Dinoki AI macOS download Dinoki AI Windows release Dinoki AI GitHub releases",{"tool_use_id":"srvtoolu_d86o01pjj5k0u6v0rm90","content":[{"title":"Osaurus | MCP Servers","url":"https://lobehub.com/de/mcp/osaurus-ai-osaurus"},{"title":"Dinoki Labs","url":"https://github.com/dinoki-ai"},{"title":"Trendshift - Ask AI","url":"https://trendshift.io/admin/repository/ask-ai/15476"},{"title":"SkillsLLM - AI Skills Marketplace","url":"https://skillsllm.com/skill/osaurus"},{"title":"Mac App 'osaurus' v0.6.9 Download","url":"https://macupdater.net/app_updates/appinfo/com.dinoki.osaurus/index.html"},{"title":"dinoki-ai/osaurus","url":"https://github.com/dinoki-ai/osaurus"},{"title":"Dinoki Documentation","url":"https://docs.dinoki.ai/"},{"title":"Getting Started | Dinoki Documentation","url":"https://docs.dinoki.ai/getting-started"},{"title":"GitHub - dinoki-ai/tweaks: AI-powered text enhancement for macOS","url":"https://github.com/dinoki-ai/tweaks"},{"title":"Support | Dinoki Documentation","url":"https://docs.dinoki.ai/support"},{"title":"Features | Dinoki Documentation","url":"https://docs.dinoki.ai/features"},{"title":"Osaurus挑战Ollama？Mac本地大模型新王者登场","url":"https://www.xugj520.cn/archives/osaurus-mac-