{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"tool_JMwp5KoLMdpJYcvEdYwmrm3l","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"Dinoki AI \"6MB\" OR \"5MB\" macOS SwiftUI screenshot pixel dinosaur\"\n\nSearch results for query: Dinoki AI 6MB macOS Dinoki AI 5MB macOS Dinoki AI SwiftUI screenshot\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"Features | Dinoki Documentation\",\"url\":\"https://docs.dinoki.ai/features\"},{\"title\":\"Getting Started | Dinoki Documentation\",\"url\":\"https://docs.dinoki.ai/getting-started\"},{\"title\":\"Building Dinoki: Native AI companion for Mac/Windows\",\"url\":\"https://www.indiehackers.com/post/building-dinoki-native-ai-companion-for-mac-windows-4228efd94a\"},{\"title\":\"Support | Dinoki Documentation\",\"url\":\"https://docs.dinoki.ai/support\"},{\"title\":\"Dinoki Documentation\",\"url\":\"https://docs.dinoki.ai/\"},{\"title\":\"Configuration | Dinoki Documentation\",\"url\":\"https://docs.dinoki.ai/configuration\"},{\"title\":\"Dinoki\",\"url\":\"https://www.aitoolnet.com/zh/dinoki\"},{\"title\":\"Dinoki: A 5MB AI Companion That Lives on Your Mac Desktop — No Servers, No Tracking\",\"url\":\"https://alternativeto.net/software/dinoki/about/\"},{\"title\":\"Dinoki for Mac v1.3.40 桌宠AI助手 人工智能同伴 宝可梦氛围 + GPT 智能\",\"url\":\"https://www.macat.vip/55458.html\"},{\"title\":\"Show HN 今日精选：2025-08-05最热门的开发者项目展示\",\"url\":\"https://showhntoday.com/show-hn-daily-roundup-2025-08-05-zh-cn\"},{\"title\":\"Dinoki for Mac v1.3.16 像素风AI 助手激活版\",\"url\":\"https://www.macqj.com/41549.html\"},{\"title\":\"Dinoki For Mac v1.2.13 桌面AI伴侣\",\"url\":\"https://macoshome.com/app/utilities/68388.html\"},{\"title\":\"Osaurus – Complete Guide to the Native AI Edge Runtime for macOS\",\"url\":\"https://addrom.com/osaurus-complete-guide-to-the-native-ai-edge-runtime-for-macos/\"},{\"title\":\"dinoki-ai/tweaks: AI-powered text enhancement for macOS\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/dinoki-ai/tweaks\"}]\n\nHere is what I found about **Dinoki AI** based on your search terms:\n\n## App Overview\n**Dinoki** is a native, lightweight AI desktop companion for macOS (and Windows) that features a pixel-art dinosaur character living on your screen. It is designed as a privacy-first alternative to bloated Electron-based AI apps.\n\n## Size & macOS Tech Stack\nThe exact size cited varies slightly by source, but both figures in your query appear:\n- **~6MB**: The official Dinoki documentation and IndieHackers post state the macOS app is **just 6MB**, built natively in **SwiftUI** (and 69MB for the Windows WPF version).\n- **Under 5MB**: Third-party listings like AlternativeTo and Mac download sites describe it as **\"under 5MB\"** or **\"less than 6MB.\"**\n\nThe lightweight size is a core selling point—official docs compare it to typical Electron AI apps that are 200MB+ downloads and use 500MB+ RAM.\n\n## The Pixel Dinosaur\n- **Character**: The default companion is **Dinoki**, a pixelated dinosaur that roams your desktop.\n- **Vibe**: Sources describe it as \"Tamagotchi vibes + GPT smarts\" and a \"pixel-art AI sidekick.\"\n- **Animations**: The character walks, jumps, plays, and interacts on screen (with basic animations included in the free version; more characters and behaviors come with Pro).\n\n## Key Features\n- **Truly Native**: SwiftUI on macOS with instant launch, minimal RAM usage (~100MB), and native OS integrations (menu bar, Retina/Metal rendering, Spaces aware).\n- **Privacy-First**: No backend server; connects directly to providers like OpenRouter, Anthropic, OpenAI, or local models via **Ollama/Osaurus**. It can work fully offline.\n- **Modes**: Chat Mode (free), Agent Mode for background tasks (Pro), and Character Mode where the dinosaur evolves autonomously (Pro).\n- **No Telemetry**: Claims no data collection, usage tracking, or screen/file access unless explicitly shared.\n\n## Sources\n- **Official Docs**: [docs.dinoki.ai](https://docs.dinoki.ai/) — confirms 6MB, SwiftUI, and native performance metrics.\n- **IndieHackers Post**: [Building Dinoki](https://www.indiehackers.com/post/building-dinoki-native-ai-companion-for-mac-windows-4228efd94a) — states \"6MB on Mac (SwiftUI), 69MB on Windows (WPF). No Electron.\"\n- **AlternativeTo**: [Dinoki listing](https://alternativeto.net/software/dinoki/about/) — describes it as \"under 5MB, SwiftUI-built.\"\n- **Mac Download Sites**: Chinese Mac app sites also cite \"less than 6MB\" and \"pixel wind\" (pixel art style) for the dinosaur.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"86674783-7214-4236-b263-658ed93960b9","uuid":"198937e6-aced-4e6f-b6e0-891cfdbc3b95","timestamp":"2026-05-20T09:39:57.117Z","tool_use_result":{"query":"Dinoki AI \"6MB\" OR \"5MB\" macOS SwiftUI screenshot pixel dinosaur","results":["Search results for query: Dinoki AI 6MB macOS Dinoki AI 5MB macOS Dinoki AI SwiftUI screenshot",{"tool_use_id":"srvtoolu_d86o2cnb28ls73f5gq70","content":[{"title":"Features | Dinoki Documentation","url":"https://docs.dinoki.ai/features"},{"title":"Getting Started | Dinoki Documentation","url":"https://docs.dinoki.ai/getting-started"},{"title":"Building Dinoki: Native AI companion for Mac/Windows","url":"https://www.indiehackers.com/post/building-dinoki-native-ai-companion-for-mac-windows-4228efd94a"},{"title":"Support | Dinoki Documentation","url":"https://docs.dinoki.ai/support"},{"title":"Dinoki Documentation","url":"https://docs.dinoki.ai/"},{"title":"Configuration | Dinoki Documentation","url":"https://docs.dinoki.ai/configuration"},{"title":"Dinoki","url":"https://www.aitoolnet.com/zh/dinoki"},{"title":"Dinoki: A 5MB AI Companion That Lives on Your Mac Desktop — No Servers, No Tracking","url":"https://alternativeto.net/software/dinoki/about/"},{"title":"Dinoki for Mac v1.3.40 桌宠AI助手 人工智能同伴 宝可梦氛围 + GPT 智能","url":"https://www.macat.vip/55458.html"},{"title":"Show HN 今日精选：2025-08-05最热门的开发者项目展示","url":"https://sho